timeline.bodyText:
Since you only assert a single report entry, you could use the new and shiny andThen(Consumer<Map.Entry<String,String>>) method. Something like this:
assertThat(results).hasNumberOfReportEntries(1).andThen(entry -> {
	assertThat(entry.getKey()).isEqualTo("stopwatch");
	assertThat(entry.getValue()).matches(format("Execution of '%s\\(\\)' took \\[[0-9]*\\] ms.", methodName));
});

